The River Dougne is the longest river in Gielinor and runs through Kandarin, a members-only kingdom. The city of Ardougne is named after this river, which begins at the Baxtorian Falls.

Contents

  • 1 Crossings
    • 1.1 By bridge
    • 1.2 By Agility
  • 2 Fishing spots
  • 3 Trivia

Crossings[edit | edit source]

By bridge[edit | edit source]

  • North of the Baxtorian Falls (the river's mouth)
  • West of the Fishing Guild
  • North of East Ardougne
  • By the entrance to Ardougne Castle
  • West of the Clock Tower
  • Near the Battlefield
  • South of the Observatory
  • Castle Wars (only accessible during the minigame)

By Agility[edit | edit source]

  • Log balance in East Ardougne (requires 33 Agility)

Fishing spots[edit | edit source]

The river has many fishing spots along it. These are:

  • At the top of the Baxtorian Falls (used for catching leaping trout, salmon and sturgeon)
  • Near the bridge north of the Combat Training Camp
  • Next to the bridge just outside Ardougne
  • Near the Observatory

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • As Ardougne, the major city on the River Dougne, is pronounced "Arr-doyn", the river itself is most likely pronounced as "Doyn".

The '''River Dougne''' is the longest [[river]] in [[Gielinor]] and runs through [[Kandarin]], a [[Members|members-only]] kingdom. The city of [[Ardougne]] is named after this river, which begins at the [[Baxtorian Falls]].

==Crossings==
===By bridge===
*North of the [[Baxtorian Falls]] (the river's mouth)
*West of the [[Fishing Guild]]
*North of [[East Ardougne]]
*By the entrance to [[Ardougne Castle]]
*West of the [[Clock Tower (building)|Clock Tower]]
*Near the [[Battlefield]]
*South of the [[Observatory]]
*[[Castle Wars]] (only accessible during the [[Minigames|minigame]])

===By Agility===
*Log balance in [[East Ardougne]] (requires 33 [[Agility]])

==Fishing spots==
The river has many [[fishing spots]] along it. These are:
*At the top of the [[Baxtorian Falls]] (used for catching [[leaping trout]], [[leaping salmon|salmon]] and [[leaping sturgeon|sturgeon]])
*Near the bridge north of the [[Combat Training Camp]]
*Next to the bridge just outside [[Ardougne]]
*Near the [[Observatory]]

==Trivia==
*As [[Ardougne]], the major city on the River Dougne, is pronounced ''"Arr-doyn"'', the river itself is most likely pronounced as ''"Doyn"''.
